title: Counter-Strike 1.6 (2016-03-21)
description:
Counter-Strike 1.6


FEATURES

- Release date 2016
- Clean rip from Steam
- Support Windows XP/Vista/7/8/8.1/10
- Protocol 48, Exe build: 4554
- Using current stable mp.dll from build 6153 (fixed animation skip issue).
- Using current stable Revolution Emulator
- Static steamid (no more steamid spoofing).
- Working server browser (Internet, Favorites, History, Spectate, Lan).
- Fully protected and customization client protector.
- Multiprotocol support. Client could join p47 servers as well as p48.
- Support unicode input/output (chat, name).
- Enabled Condtion Zero stuff (BOTs, hostage, grenade drop, c4 icon).
- MasterServer with trusted servers.
- Playable on Internet and LAN
- In game ads are removed
- Auto redirect with cmd /server
- Stable & Clear release!

Have a nice game play !
